<PrivacyLayout appSlug="voicelog" lastUpdated="2026-05-17">

  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <p>VoiceLog runs Whisper transcription on your device. Your audio recordings and their transcripts never leave your phone. There is no account, no server upload, no third-party analytics.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>On-device only:</strong> audio recordings, their transcripts, and AI-generated reflection summaries. All stored locally in the app's sandboxed storage.</li>
    <li><strong>Microphone permission:</strong> required to record. Audio is processed locally and discarded after transcription unless you choose to keep it.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No audio is uploaded to any server.</li>
    <li>No transcripts are uploaded.</li>
    <li>No account, no login, no email.</li>
    <li>No advertising or analytics SDKs.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>AI reflection</h2>
  <p>If on-device AI (Gemini Nano) is available on your device, reflections are generated locally. On devices without on-device AI, reflection features are disabled.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>Everything lives on your device. Uninstall to delete. Export available in-app for plain-text backup.</p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>VoiceLog is not directed at children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>Updates flagged via the date above and in-app.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p><a href="mailto:hello@brooo.app">hello@brooo.app</a></p>

</PrivacyLayout>
